title: [ Community Choice ITO 1 ]  —— Evanesco
body:
ITO (Initial Twitter Offering) is a new feature Mask Network developed at the beginning of 2021. Individuals and organizations can conduct decentralized asset offering directly on social media, and users could participate in a token offering directly on Twitter.

Since inception, we designed ITO to be permissionless for all internet users. Individuals and projects could choose to launch a permissionless or a community choice ITO. To help people make better use of ITO, Mask Network introduced a community voting mechanism and formed ITO Review Committee (learn more  https://news.mask.io/zh-Hans/2021/04/22/ito-is-upgraded-who-is-the-next ), to benefit the growth of the Mask Network ecosystem with the help of the community.

We opened up applications for the ITO Review Committee and ITO Projects on April 22nd. On April 27th, 11 $MASK holders were selected out of more than 40 applicants and formed the first ITO Review Committee.

Evanesco Network is the first project that applied for ITO since we introduced the community voting mechanism. After a thorough examination and sufficient communication with the project, the decision to pass the preliminary review was made carefully by the Committee.

Now we will begin the third step of a community choice ITO ---- $MASK Voting

The Snapshot vote will last for 36 hours, all $MASK holders could vote “Yes” or “No” on this ITO. The quorum is 100,000 $MASK (the vote is not valid until there are at least 100,000 votes), with a more than 66.67% approval ratio (Numbers could be changed in the future). 


EVA ITO Plan

1st Round
Amount: 100,000 USDT
Price: 0.03
Max buying amount (single address): 800 USDT
Tokens available to swap: $ETH; $MASK; $USDT
 
Whitelist requirements (only need to meet one of them)
1. $MASK holder at a certain time (please provide a snapshot as proof), hold more than 50 $MASK, retweet and follow EVA’s official Twitter account (@evanescoio), join EVA’s official Telegram group chat
2. Community events: 15 ITO whitelist positions 
3. Social Media: follow EVA’s official Twitter and retweet the promotion tweet; Refer your friends (e.g. 5) to join the official Telegram group chat.
( EVA will release more details on how to confirm these actions )

2nd Round
Amount: 200,000 USDT
Price: 0.03
Max buying amount (single address): 400 USDT
Tokens available to swap: $ETH; $USDT; other
1. Follow EVA Twitter (@evanescoio), and retweet the event tweet, join the official Telegram group chat
( EVA will release more details on how to confirm these actions )

Airdrop
There will be airdrop to addresses that participated in the ITO. Details to follow soon.
